Search Across All Tabs: Who said you could only search one tab at a time? Oh, that's right, your web browser did. Well, not anymore. Ctrl-F Plus laughs in the face of limitations.

Feels Like Home: Designed to look and act like the native find function, Ctrl-F Plus is like the cool cousin who came to visit and never left. And you love it.

Simplicity is Key: No complicated setups, no eye-rolling procedures. Just press Ctrl-Shift-F and type in what you're looking for. Because you have better things to do with your time.
